# Image to BW Altium Converter

A powerful utility to convert color images (PNG, JPEG, BMP, etc.) into high-quality 1-bit black-and-white PNGs using Floydâ€“Steinberg error diffusion. This repository provides both a simple CLI tool and a modern GUI frontend.

